    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 15.27,
    "end": 20.37,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "戰士們注意我們正式進入「酸鹼鹽」的大魔王關卡",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 20.57,
    "end": 24.99,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "老師講義上寫著「強酸會完全解離」",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 25.19,
    "end": 28.54,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "可是這不代表它一定很酸嗎",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 28.74,
    "end": 33.95,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "沒錯這可是超常考的文字陷阱",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 34.15,
    "end": 39.01,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "強酸只代表它溶於水會百分之百解離",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 39.21,
    "end": 42.65,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "但如果我們只拿一小滴的強酸",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 42.85,
    "end": 46.96,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "滴進整整一百公升的純水游泳池裡",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 47.16,
    "end": 52.04,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "哇那這樣濃度就被稀釋得超級低耶",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 52.24,
    "end": 56.26,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "所以到底酸不酸、會不會腐蝕",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 56.46,
    "end": 59.92,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "完全是由「濃度」來決定的",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 60.12,
    "end": 64.71,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "喔所以弱酸雖然只有部分解離",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 64.91,
    "end": 68.42,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "但如果是濃度極高的冰醋酸",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 68.62,
    "end": 72.18,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "不小心碰到一樣會受重傷對吧",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
